!!Welcome to ChatArchivist Version 0.6

ChatArchivist is a tool used to provide a medium for users, researchers, and educators to explore, develop, and reflect on the ethical and effective use of artificial intelligence by having a place to gather, document and annotate their unique experiences. 
This tool uses [[TiddlyWiki|http://www.tiddlywiki.com]], an open source platform, to import and provide access to an archive of chatGPT messages, generated by OpenAI. See [[Using TiddlyWiki]].

